```plantuml
@startuml tarhses_esp-alarm-clock

actor User
participant "Main Task" as Main
participant "Network Task" as Network
participant "Alarm Task" as Alarm
participant "Display Task" as Display
participant "Sound Task" as Sound
participant "Potentiometer Task" as Pot
participant "Storage" as Storage

User -> Pot: Adjust potentiometers
Pot -> Alarm: Send alarm time (via queue)
Alarm -> Display: Update alarm display (via event)

Main -> Storage: Read config.json
Storage --> Main: Return WiFi/NTP config
Main -> Network: Initialize WiFi
Network -> Network: Connect to WiFi
Network -> Network: Sync time via SNTP
Network -> Display: Update time display (periodic event)

User -> Alarm: Toggle alarm switch
Alarm -> Display: Update alarm status icon

Alarm -> Alarm: Check current time vs alarm
Alarm -> Sound: Trigger alarm sound (via event)
Sound -> Storage: Get random audio file
Storage --> Sound: Return audio file path
Sound -> Sound: Play alarm sound

User -> Alarm: Press button (snooze/stop)
Alarm -> Sound: Stop alarm sound (via event)
Alarm -> Display: Update alarm status

@enduml
```